sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Merchant POS
    participant C as CardFlow
    participant B as Bank
    
    M->>C: Submit Transaction
    activate C
    C->>C: Validate Data
    C->>B: Request Authorization
    activate B
    B->>B: Check Funds
    B-->>C: Auth Response
    deactivate B
    C->>C: Log Transaction
    C-->>M: Transaction Result
    deactivate C
